Add `devServer &gt; disableHostCheck` in `vue.config.js`
```javascript
module.exports = {
  //...
  devServer: {
    disableHostCheck: true,
  }
}
```

Reference:
- https://github.com/vuejs-templates/webpack/issues/1205
- https://blog.csdn.net/guzhao593/article/details/85918869
